item.title: CVE-2018-11052|2024-09-17T04:00:07.900Z -- dell%20emc -- ecs
item.description: Dell EMC ECS versions 3.2.0.0 and 3.2.0.1 contain an authentication bypass vulnerability. A remote unauthenticated attacker could exploit this vulnerability to read and modify S3 objects by supplying specially crafted S3 requests.
